reviewText: I can't get it to play, even on something that isn't region locked.

Awesome! Not as loyal to the manga as I would have hoped. Because a movie, favorite characters like Komaki were placed in the background, but still, if you are big fan of Library Wars, totally worth it.
Nice film a lot more action than the original.
I loved this movie so much, I had to read the manga and watch the anime versions as well. It is funny and fast-paced and smart.
